        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-6">
            Birmingham's renaissance has made it a destination. BJCC hosts major concerts, conventions, and sporting events. UAB brings students, families, and medical visitors year-round. The city's award-winning food scene, civil rights history, and cultural attractions draw tourists from around the world.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Downtown lofts, Southside apartments, Five Points South condos, and even homes in Homewood and Mountain Brook are thriving as short-term rentals. Business travelers, event attendees, and tourists all need somewhere to stay—and they expect hotel-quality cleanliness.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our turnover cleaning ensures your Birmingham rental maintains the 5-star ratings that keep bookings coming. We handle everything from fresh linens to spotless bathrooms so you can focus on growing your rental business.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
